{"tid":807784,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《墓場物語》有無人玩?","createTime":"2018-09-05T21:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T04:46:03.000Z","uid":198148,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52b1f5626907d9ec667b613deab520f5a6ac6d70","tid":807784,"uid":198148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T21:08:40.000Z","msg":"同牧場物語有7成相似<br />\n<br />\n詳情: <a href=\"https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99002698/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamebase.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ftopic%2F99002698%2F&d=6fMU2XtVQY4ofq32ISlMYghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f03548d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99002698/</a><br />\n<br />\nsteam $89 好似係<br />\n<br />\n可能有D難上手<br />\n<br />\n但鐘意玩牧場物語既你呢隻GAME應該岩你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係岩岩玩左無耐 一齊鳩流下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eda86fa665b9005b6ab0b77dfd05dc0aa61c4fa","tid":807784,"uid":121868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T22:49:01.000Z","msg":"應該幾過癮,<br />\n但3200個review, 有1200個正皮, 1000個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係睇定啲先"},{"pid":"1a60596e3db59f9cd5b8893acc5b77b22f633f86","tid":807784,"uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:15:19.000Z","msg":"想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但睇評價好兩極化咁<br />\n巴打有冇咩分享"},{"pid":"5e9db9183ec5a073e936f921883de1ca719b73cb","tid":807784,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:25:27.000Z","msg":"睇過gameplay 啲人話抄星露谷物語好多原素 同埋個體力系統好鳩 做幾下野就要訓覺 到後期整到野食先得 <br />\n行路慢 仲有買得多野加價變貴 賣得多野降價賺少<br />\n總之就係幾鳩嘅系統<br />\n利申 冇玩過"},{"pid":"55026e0be6dc711d5c64767b2c4eaea4bf9d28c3","tid":807784,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"暗黑版農場物語"},{"pid":"a19060767b7a3176ba7e3a5f722773ea1669adea","tid":807784,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"好多野未開,半成品GAME,廣告話有吸血鬼/入新城全部冇<br />\n爆機之後講明D野賣DLC<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d0978e56a29a8cdd533f2214476e922be02dc6","tid":807784,"uid":72932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"差唔多玩爆 一開始的確難玩 冇乜指示 多材料 背包細 體力少 玩到後期啲嘢整哂出黎就就易玩好多 <br />\n<br />\n不過其實同牧場物語好唔同 呢個game係比較有劇情有目的咁玩 每日好多嘢做咁 除左有得種菜 唔知點解會話佢似牧場物語<br />\n<br />\n想玩牧場物語就唔好買呢隻 stardew valley比較適合你"}]}